        "auto_route": true,
        "strict_route": false,
        "stack": "gvisor",
        "sniff": true
      }
```

**Temporary workaround:**
Disable auto-refresh or set log to file or change log level to error/warn.

**Possible cause:**
Log message output too frequent to log scroll view, each new line trigger OnPaint event and new line concat to scroll box content, this process is very inefficient and trigger lots of window refresh events and CPU resources which slows GUI responsiveness.

**Possible improvements:**
Implement a fast refresh scrollview with double buffer or change refresh mechanism, such as filter display log message by level or buffered output instead of per-line output.


